---
title: Creamy Mustard Chicken with Spinach Mashed Potato
description: Serve up a comforting meal that's as good as a hug! With a flavoursome creamy mustard sauce and loads of satisfying mash, this dinner will make you feel all snuggly – perfect for a home-cooked meal with heart.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-leek-mustard-chicken-6226b6c8.jpg
